<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Least_common_multiple">Least common multiple</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Greatest_common_divisor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Least common multiple"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1320445320" /><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Further information: <a href="/wiki/Least_common_multiple" title="Least common multiple">Least common multiple</a></div>
